{"tid":1458622,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"喂屌,咪撚再捉鬼住! 消息開始出事比人利用同誤傷","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:08:26.000Z","uid":69864,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"40295663bfa4b3da0b89d4a22fc8aac22e87f4c3","tid":1458622,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:31:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">呢幾日係FACEBOOK開始不斷咁有人傳<br />\n咩咩係警犬扮,<br />\n咩咩咩係臥底,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">鬼唔係唔捉得</span>,<br />\n但一定要係有<span style=\"color: orange;\">100%肯定性既證據</span>先好SHARE同推。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">原因一(誤傷手足):</div><br />\n今日機場單野<span style=\"color: gold;\">何韻詩個<ins>女助手</ins></span>因為剪左個短頭髮就比人係黃絲PAGE<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><ins>狂推做係女警</ins></span>。<br />\n呢個事主都叫做有小小知名度,先比人證明到係自己人,但你地有冇諗過果d普通手足?<br />\n隨時比藍絲反利用黎屈做鬼去離間我地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsFw14b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsFw14b.png&h=1a12c8b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLINK:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/317007248423308/photos/pcb.1343505799106776/1343505682440121/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F317007248423308%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.1343505799106776%2F1343505682440121%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=e31414f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/317007248423308/photos/pcb.1343505799106776/1343505682440121/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">原因二(被警方利用定性):</div><br />\n大家有冇諗過如果連我地都話放火,衝擊立法會,玩磚既人係鬼,<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係暴徒</span></strong><br />\n但最後比人發現唔係, 原來真係義士黎既話。<br />\n即係連你都認同佢地係暴徒,完全係中左中共統戰分化撚既計。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連自己都要自己係恐怖分子?</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">原因三(核彈不割):</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">放核彈都唔割洗唔洗再解釋?</span><br />\n我地唔係老共,唔好因為FACEBOOK上面小小你證實唔到既消息就亂同人割。<br />\n同鬼割係冇問題,但我真係真心希望大家真係要有充份證據先好去講人係鬼,<br />\n何謂充份證據? 最好係無剪接影片/清楚既相片入面有當時人,有當時人著警員制服照片(小心PS查清來源) 呢個已經係最低要求。 其他幾張圖就指證,小心誤傷自己人。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">原因四(目標失焦):</div><br />\n我唔知大家Facebook同我個Facebook有冇分別,我依家見到成個Wall有5成以上都係捉鬼,<br />\n大家請記住, <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">五大訴求先係我地真正既目的</span></strong></span> 。<br />\n記住, 我地<ins>唔係黎玩捉鬼online</ins><br />\n係連登推一個你信任得過既冷氣軍師post,好過你係facebook屌人係鬼<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">補充:</div><br />\n我知有人可能會覺得令大眾市民認為 「玩火玩石玩攻城」既人係警犬會有幫助。<br />\n但如果證據不足, 呢啲野真係隨時反彈, 比對家利用黎吸收更多支持者。<br />\n所以唔係請大家唔好捉鬼, 而係唔好因為事件G有人100%證明到有警犬扮示威者, 就去證明事件B既人係警犬扮。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121b26aafa6b690c2dec73b1103a8aed6158ad50","tid":1458622,"uid":214036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78ab29fb3d9b8d4d6dc5a80699a4998ef4019e78","tid":1458622,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"希望大家理智咁放返焦點去「聽日有咩活動」身上<br />\n<br />\n鬼要捉,但有其他仲緊要既消息要大家去發放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nEg. 女義士文宣, 機場點玩既集思廣益, 玩警嫂, 其他文宣"},{"pid":"707089b8aad29fab1b552a2902942370cfd5a53c","tid":1458622,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:44.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要小心比人分化"},{"pid":"e4a04a8922b7b4789022db9cadbec20ebf1c11ab","tid":1458622,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121b26aafa6b690c2dec73b1103a8aed6158ad50","tid":1458622,"uid":214036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T1